e blank\u2019 and it is.\u00a0&lt;\/li&gt;\t&lt;\/ul&gt;&lt;\/li&gt;&lt;\/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you for any feedback that you can provide.\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/community.intercom.com\/product-tours-10\/product-tour-pointer-for-fill-in-the-blank-not-functioning-properly-4695&quot;,&quot;creationDate&quot;:&quot;2023-07-03T21:31:26+0000&quot;,&quot;relativeCreationDate&quot;:&quot;6 days ago&quot;},&quot;numberOfViews&quot;:6,&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;question&quot;,&quot;featuredImage&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;publicLabel&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;\/product-area-5&quot;,&quot;categoryId&quot;:5,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Product Area&quot;,&quot;metaRobots&quot;:&quot;index, follow&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:0},&quot;lastPostId&quot;:&quot;9022&quot;},{&quot;firstPost&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:4694,&quot;author&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:11078,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;\/members\/halil-yildirim-11078&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Halil Yildirim&quot;,&quot;avatar&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;userTitle&quot;:&quot;New Participant&quot;,&quot;rank&quot;:{&quot;isBold&quot;:false,&quot;isItalic&quot;:false,&quot;isUnderline&quot;:false,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;New Participant&quot;},&quot;userLevel&quot;:0},&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;We are sending user data from Segment to DAST, we did all the mapping according to the documentations and did not exceed limitations but still some of the event properties we receive with the event is not visible on the user profile. e.g We are sending \u201corder_completed\u201d event and can see \u201cinvoice_url\u201d in the custom properties list but not seeing it on the user profile.&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/community.intercom.com\/apps-integrations-25\/segment-events-are-not-appearing-on-the-user-profile-even-after-received-4694&quot;,&quot;creationDate&quot;:&quot;2023-07-03T15:16:33+0000&quot;,&quot;relativeCreationDate&quot;:&quot;6 days ago&quot;},&quot;